trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the collection of chain elements is synchronized.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om samling av kjede elementer er synkronisert.

trans-unit.source: This value is always `false` because an <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ChainElementCollection> object is not thread safe.
trans-unit.target: Denne verdien er alltid `false` fordi en <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ChainElementCollection>objektet er ikke trygt tråd.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509ChainElementCollection>
